{"tid":470126,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大生畢業禮舉示威標語　沈祖堯寄語學生：下結論前應坐下想清楚","createTime":"2017-11-16T04:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T06:04:42.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ae32cb7b095117320e6b267a5662b1d81863da43","tid":470126,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171116/s00001/9c112ab5a969c804130adba1766d17f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171116%2Fs00001%2F9c112ab5a969c804130adba1766d17f2.jpg&h=a45654cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天是中文大學畢業禮，有社會科學院畢業生在被頒授學位期間，戴上畫有紅色交叉的口罩，分別手持印「捍衛學界言論自由」的紙張，另有人高舉印有禁止符號及寫着「DON'T SILENCE ME」的紙張。<br />\n<br />\n去年同樣有學生在畢業禮播行國歌時，舉起印有反「釋」的紙張，2014年經歷佔領運動，亦有畢業生舉起黃傘。<br />\n<br />\n校長沈祖堯在畢業典禮致辭時表示自己是最後一次以校長身份主持畢業典禮。他憶述自己在2010年正式上任後，經歷學制改革、人事變動、校園爭議及社會動盪等，又難忘在中大百萬大道2次看世界盃決賽播放。他表示社會上有不同意見，寄語學生應多聆聽，又指許多事情非表面看起來般簡單，如政治爭論及道德議題，鼓勵學生在下結論前應先「坐下及想清楚（sit down and think）」。<br />\n<br />\n沈又說批評別人是一件容易的事，引用「話到口中留半句，理從是處讓三分」勸勉學生說話應留有餘地；更指不當說話會星火燎原，不當行為則會後悔一生。他感概自己「在過去7年學會許多」，認為「能在此時為中大人服務」是其榮幸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171116/s00001/1510801924765\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171116%2Fs00001%2F1510801924765&d=f5FGq3ggdxP5DuSvVviHgZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=e2e6a902\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171116%2Fs00001%2F1510801924765&h=94394e30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171116/s00001/1510801924765</a>"},{"pid":"44f1af2aa9541fca635ce2a71ccc4bdf08cddd17","tid":470126,"uid":22858,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:22:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">收皮啦</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/VAN/ftp/News/20141003/HK/_03GZ006_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FVAN%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20141003%2FHK%2F_03GZ006_.jpg&h=ea4d6527&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d022873bd86aef2c976cd5bfed7c29b2b110dbd","tid":470126,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:23:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0bf4d4e3f6dc138a75df26d7336d1c7548e0cc7","tid":470126,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:26:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5abe89775b607c37bf829c6665c2e52dc5777229","tid":470126,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:28:08.000Z","msg":"沈祖堯out 啦，而家係有風駛盡、有權用盡、落水狗要打盡"},{"pid":"0578d1e2b90f189db49635d82345310a913e17d2","tid":470126,"uid":128261,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沈祖堯out 啦，而家係有風駛盡、有權用盡、落水狗要打盡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n「話到口中留半句，理從是處讓三分」<br />\n又話殺無赦、又話買唔到樓應該走、又話放棄年輕人、又話月入少過14000蚊唔應該有投票權、又話公屋要封頂、又話未富先驕、又話要包容大小便<br />\n又唔見沈校長講下呢7年黎高官權貴講過既以上仆街野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日叫學生包容"},{"pid":"8aee32eb2e38fff63f3182c5214cbd48ce101f31","tid":470126,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T06:04:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家言論唔自由咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/140439_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F140439_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a0029207&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}